body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/470\n\nShorthand date filters for agent loops: `pm list --today` (updated today) and `pm list --recent` (updated in the last 7 days) as sugar over --updated-after, avoiding ISO-timestamp construction. Wire per the new-flag checklist (contracts, completions, docs, MCP param parity)."
